Description of the project goals

As a [description of user],
I want [functionality]
so that [benefit].

User story #1
- As a Telegram user, I want to record audio-message to Bot to get what i told from Bot in a text message.

User story #2
- Also as a Telegram user, I want to find text message using words which were said so that i could get full message with those words.

User story #3
- Also as a Telegram user, I want to write a message to get this message with the translation

    Used technologies

- Convert Audio to Text with Google Cloud Speech API.
- Text Translation with Google Translate API in Python.
